How to run

Install deps:

pip install requests urllib3 PyYAML


Scan a single group by path or ID:

python gitlab_inventory_report_all_groups_v2.py \
  --base-url https://gitlab.example.com \
  --token <YOUR_PAT> \
  --group-name parent/subgroup \
  --out gitlab_projects_report_mygroup.csv


Scan the entire instance (everything visible to your token):

python gitlab_inventory_report_all_groups_v2.py \
  --base-url https://gitlab.example.com \
  --token <YOUR_PAT> \
  --out gitlab_projects_report_all.csv \
  --scan-scope my


Admins can truly scan all instance groups:

python gitlab_inventory_report_all_groups_v2.py \
  --base-url https://gitlab.example.com \
  --token <ADMIN_PAT_WITH_read_api> \
  --out gitlab_projects_report_all.csv \
  --scan-scope all


python user_contribution_report.py --group-name "dev-team" --token <PAT> --disable-ssl-verify
